Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都喜歡著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}定是…從我們初遇起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是那啥嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結果是白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那句話昨天也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這種地方睡覺也會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和學姐成為戀人的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是現實哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得還讓人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多虧了谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓我注意到了自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川 身體還不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還腫著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個樣子怎麼去見大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼好在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又沒變多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個 你和大家說了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之說是得了熱感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 還算妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 誰叫我是你的青梅竹馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 前天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我誰都沒說 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 快到吃午飯的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎吃完再走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎說有事馬上就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在…那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是叫北原同學吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然是同一個小學的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是一個班還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫谷川柑菜 往後請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又在一個班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全沒什麼改善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這是石垣哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請多關照 北原美櫻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的…名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 認識麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 女生的名字和長相我全都記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該說你勤快呢還是說你傻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就不能解釋為我是女權紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是花了很長時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多餘的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從那之後 已經三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪裡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去探望柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是別去為好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在那傢伙的眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}眼感？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是不想把感冒傳染給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連我也不讓去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你去了柑菜那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為是青梅竹馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正探望的蛋糕也不能浪費掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 不過是粗茶淡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想整理一下膠片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐拍了很多回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擠了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事就不可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊 好像喜歡靠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人不喜歡這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也…不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請別在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就那樣繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果真在一起了 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 你突然說了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打著拍攝的幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了呢 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學 這是我給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定要好好珍惜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這如同奇蹟的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 吃飽了吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然美櫻的蛋糕很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也就這點優點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有優點就很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲郎也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身材高挑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}相貌堂堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手又靈巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很擅長記女孩子的長相和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那些算不上優點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可以問你一件不好問的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要邀請貴月學姐參與電影製作？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為海他 貌似想要我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是沒想到學姐會答應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你和她處得那麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連我都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不可能不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要邀請貴月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是學姐和霧島同學變得親密的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說了不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是想著要支持海 才向學姐搭話的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在想如果柑菜能參與電影製作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就能縮短與海間的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然不知道這會變成什麼結果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是打算兩邊都支持的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話 哲朗你的心意該何去何從？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你對柑菜的心意又該何去何從？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你那什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直看在眼裡 所以我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗的眼裡一直都只有柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要對自己說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再繼續那樣逃避下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}時間也不會幫你解決問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「有什麼想說的就說出來吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對我說這番話的不是哲朗你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我才鼓起了勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然那時候說了不用回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但現在能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對你…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我…現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會和往常一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起開開心心的拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍好了以後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在校園文化節之類上放…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會做回平常那個谷川柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川她今天來我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我到底 能做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好痛…

Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等喝點水後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.02,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在日本泡澡完後習慣要補充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起去散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 難得一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就在想晚上也會很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…而且這也是我們的回憶之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有這麼多的自然景觀被保留了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好奇怪啊 明明是第一次來的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}卻有種讓人懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重新問一下 能不能讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也幫忙去尋找那個「地方」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 也想為學姐盡一份力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實 我是以那為目的而來到這個星球的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒不如說 是想以這次旅行為契機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並不是因為有什麼事發生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才想要做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 想用這個開始一段什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看看自己能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們都一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話 我就更加想要實現學姐的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在 我只想和海人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想和海人 和大家 一起拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就是我現在的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我早已明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這個世界上不存在永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為是外星人所以不行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為不能一直呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以無法回應海人的心意是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就打算用著這樣的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直從海人身邊逃開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為海人得以如願以償了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣就…夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說 你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回來之後 就一直沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找姐姐我商量商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先說了 你就這點不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}保持沉默可不能解決問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}光耍帥是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看似活得無懈可擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但在我看來不過是個小屁孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑回娘家的人別那麼自豪的談論人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是回娘家 是離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說 我還有地方可以回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}夫妻吵架也是有很多種類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 沒和女生交往過的你是不會懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡有一股處男味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你就快回…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}受你關照了哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之 你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的~好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}切 又是這德行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我打算後天重新開始拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以是可以啦 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你難道說已經和學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 關於那個我會在和大家見面時說清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 柑菜要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我才更加要說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在…幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的話明天的拍攝就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒問題 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 有電話找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹什麼啊 把我叫來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我姑且也算是大病初愈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係吧 腫也消了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好！魔術牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幼稚園的時候 常聽到這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候明明是我比較高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼時候就差了這麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前我被欺負的時候還老給你救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜飛拳是無敵的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很帥氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊 講的這麼噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 你不是為了講這些小時候的事才叫我出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來你的腳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有…有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要緊話是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是海人的事 那就不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我多少知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果沒別的事我就回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得你和海要是能順利就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我卻不想看到這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想啊 如果海和學姐能順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就能恢復自由什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做著這樣無謂的期待啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明不會有…這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隨意捉弄著自己喜歡的女孩…甚至最後還惹哭她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}卻什麼也做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}騙…騙人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從什麼時候起？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的…在我腦袋亂糟糟的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然說些什麼呢！笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是 時機選的很差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…終於說出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白的 你喜歡海的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即便海喜歡一夏學姐 也依然如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是喜歡這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就自己把想說的話都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一副自我滿足的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別忍耐 柑菜保持柑菜的原樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不要隨便摸女孩子的頭髮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要我說你也明白的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哭出來也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說啊 你來這裡犯規了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩子可是不屈不撓的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果有了喜歡的人 會變得堅強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我多虧了哲朗 變了好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…至少我變得想要去改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變得有了這些想望…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這話該由我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感冒已經好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要吃…西瓜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從很久之前就喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 願意聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影 要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倘若世事無常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吾心依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}攝影機OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這邊也好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第275個景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 黑衣人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(720,666)}Black man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我還想呆在這個星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這星球上有對我很重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐說 今天直到傍晚都要好好拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還要拍多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.03,0:23:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得在暑假內能拍完的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有一周嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還活著啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你知道我有多擔心你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐…姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐為什麼到地球來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是那個啦 肯定是來祝福我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊呀討厭 姐姐真性急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是這樣麼

